    <title>なぜ「価値を引き継ぐ人」が必要になるのか | VCDesign Companion</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/page-shell.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/reading.css">
    <style>
